{{Quote|Lieutenant, the embassy is ''secure''. Open the landing pads and notify the delegates we're open for business.|[[Gregar Typho/Legends|Gregar Typho]]|<ref name="Too Many Cooks">{{SWComicCite|7.4|Too Many Cooks}}</ref>}}
The '''Naboo Embassy''' was the permanent representation of the [[Royal House of Naboo/Legends|Royal House of Naboo]] to the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], and was located on on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

==History==
Occupied by the delegation from [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] following the [[Chommell sector/Legends|Chommell sector's]] acceptance into the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] circa [[800 BBY/Legends|800 BBY]], the Embassy served as a place for all Naboo immigrants living on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] to visit and speak with their representatives. The headquarters of all Naboo activity on Coruscant, the building was located just southwest of the [[Senate Building/Legends|Senate Building]] and [[Monument Plaza/Legends|Monument Plaza]].<ref name="Hnn-BREAKING NEWS: Amidala Alive / BREAKING NEWS: Amidala Attacked">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|56|news/13516_1.html|BREAKING NEWS: Amidala Alive / BREAKING NEWS: Amidala Attacked}}</ref>

In [[52 BBY/Legends|52 BBY]] the [[Funeral/Legends|funeral]] of [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Vidar Kim]] was held at the embassy, his body cremated after a viewing ceremony and his ashes returned to Naboo by his colleague, [[Janus Greejatus/Legends|Janus Greejatus]].<ref name="SWDP" />

